// ============================================================================
//  REMOTE.cpp
//  Polar Antenna Remote Panel (HB9IIU
//  -----------------------------------
//  ESP32 + CYD TFT display + KY-040 encoder
//  Handles local antenna selection and synchronizes with CLUB via MQTT.
//
//  Features:
//   - TFT mirror display of club polar map and antenna state
//   - Rotary encoder for antenna selection
//   - MQTT communication with CLUB_SWITCH controller
//   - Touchscreen to toggle between dial and great-circle map
//   - WiFi and MQTT status indicators
//   - OTA firmware updates via ElegantOTA
//
//  Author : Daniel / HB9IIU
//  Date   : 2025-12-17
// ============================================================================

